@startuml sd_DepartmentService_getTree
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title DepartmentService.getTree() - 获取部门树形结构

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "DepartmentController" as Ctrl
participant "DepartmentService" as Service
participant "DepartmentRepository" as Repo
participant "Department\n(实体)" as Entity

Client -> Ctrl: GET /api/departments
Ctrl -> Service: getTree()
Service -> Repo: findByParentIsNull()
Repo --> Service: List<Department>\n(仅顶级部门)
Service --> Ctrl: 返回树形结果\n(懒加载子部门)
Ctrl --> Client: ApiResponse<List<Department>>
note right of Entity : Lazy加载 children\n自动填充子部门列表
@enduml
